{"tid":1769197,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【神巧合】網民以《冰雪奇緣2》暗喻抗爭運動：五大元素代表五大訴求","createTime":"2019-12-04T16:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T17:30:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf36f2a0217f38043448f89f8b3e3a4635fb1d8","tid":1769197,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_712252_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_712252_0&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=efb3075d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_712252_0&h=aafbacb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_712252_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【神巧合】網民以《冰雪奇緣2》暗喻抗爭運動：五大元素代表五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20191204/1536pix/1575453062_d14a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20191204%2F1536pix%2F1575453062_d14a.png&h=9f88e7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風靡萬千兒童的迪士尼動畫電影《冰雪奇緣2》，日前在港上畫，有網民睇完之後，發現劇情竟與香港目前的抗爭運動十分相似，並以香港情況融入電影畫面中，當中Elsa與Anna分別代表勇武及和理非，國王King Agnarr則代表泛民，並將不少抗爭運動中所發生的事件「連結」其中，例如「叫咗你哋唔好搞亂一國兩制」、「貿易戰」、「火魔法」等，並以五大元素代表五大訴求，尤其以佩比爺爺（Grand Pabbie）「飾演」的蕭生，最為「入型入格」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有網民將《冰雪奇緣2》的劇情「簡化」，「套戲係講有座城市表面和平繁榮，暗裡卻隱藏極大的危機，有股強大的力量及聲音干擾來自北方，女主角堅持要求獨立調查，只有查到真相，城市才會得到安寧。過程之中有人多次表不不割席，要齊上齊落，眾人北上過程中，不斷被煙霧和水馬阻擋，而且更經常有召喚火魔法及水魔法，女主角及後發現五大元素缺一不可，並揭發政權殺害魔法師的真相。最後更喚醒及煽動很多人掟石及對大型基建作出大規模破壞，最後城市才得以重生。」網民更抵死表示：「聽講有好多家長帶小朋友去睇添」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRJnNki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRJnNki.jpg&h=d5a874eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPUKgdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPUKgdE.jpg&h=3080ee1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSrgRM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSrgRM0.jpg&h=5643fcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucB40Fk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucB40Fk.jpg&h=845a8ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BukNd0m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBukNd0m.jpg&h=329f634e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ced4dd9f19a5d2c1a13d7db6953d4e56870fbef","tid":1769197,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14eaf59baa9a4ea0b01bb511ca67df61773623b2","tid":1769197,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"燒山嗰張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd5bf36fe5623cfaba25ebb367a2bccaa29f2ef","tid":1769197,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a83fc97e92dfb97eca69fb2d7b9523dff62b0fcc","tid":1769197,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1954ae883e8d12b7fc43fdf92409b0ad0106ebf8","tid":1769197,"uid":50740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"支那會唔會小氣到禁播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c5133411a98cb5660ddd6eb41edd7493f594bd","tid":1769197,"uid":313203,"like":2,"d